videos.headline: Green with the QB option for a 10-yard TD run
videos.description: Marshall's QB Isaiah Green keep the ball on the option play and runs it in for a 10 yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Johnson punches it in for the score after the big turnover
videos.description: Marshall's Darius Hodge takes a bad snap by South Florida to the 1 yard line and Artis Johnson runs it in for the score.

videos.headline: McCants with the 38 yard strike to St. Felix
videos.description: South Florida's Tyre McCants hits Randall St. Felix for a 38 yard touchdown

videos.headline: Randall St. Felix catches his second TD
videos.description: Blake Barnett complete the deep touchdown pass to Randall St. Felix to bring South Florida within 2 scores.
